─────────────────────\n300: T1.1-T7.3 ──┬── T8.1-T8.8 (all tests)\n301: ```\n302: \n303: ---\n304: \n305: ## Verification Commands\n306: \n307: | Task | Verification Command |\n308: |------|----------------------|\n309: | Phase 1 | `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\"` |\n310: | Phase 2 | `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep -A20 \"name: workloadmanager\"` |\n311: | Phase 3 | `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep -A20 \"name: agentcube-router\"` |\n312: | Phase 4 | `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=test-sa | grep \"kind: Role\"` |\n313: | Phase 5 | `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true | grep \"vc-agent-scheduler\"` |\n314: | Phase 6 | `kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f manifests/charts/base/crds/` |\n315: | Phase 7 | `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base 2>&1` (should fail without redis.addr) |\n316: | Phase 8 | `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" && helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" > /tmp/rendered.yaml && kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f /tmp/rendered.yaml` |\n317: \n318: ---\n319: \n320: ## Acceptance Criteria\n321: \n322: - [ ] `Chart.yaml` with name, version, appVersion, description, keywords, maintainers, sources\n323: - [ ] `values.yaml` with redis.addr, redis.password, imagePullSecrets, nameOverride, fullnameOverride\n324: - [ ] `values.yaml` with workloadmanager.* (replicas, image, service, resources, extraEnv)\n325: - [ ] `values.yaml` with router.* (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rbac.create)\n326: - [ ] `values.yaml` with volcano.scheduler.* (enabled, replicas, image)\n327: - [ ] `_helpers.tpl` with agentcube.name, agentcube.fullname, agentcube.labels, agentcube.selectorLabels, agentcube.image\n328: - [ ] WorkloadManager Deployment template with configurable replicas, image, resources, env, probes\n329: - [ ] WorkloadManager Service template with configurable type and port\n330: - [ ] Router Deployment template with configurable replicas, image, resources, env, probes, serviceAccountName\n331: - [ ] Router Service template with configurable port and targetPort\n332: - [ ] WorkloadManager RBAC (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) with full permissions\n333: - [ ] Router RBAC (ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding) conditionally rendered\n334: - [ ] Volcano scheduler resources conditionally rendered\n335: - [ ] AgentRuntime CRD with maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, podTemplate, targetPort\n336: - [ ] CodeInterpreter CRD with authMode, maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, template, warmPoolSize\n337: - [ ] Template fails if redis.addr not provided\n338: - [ ] Template fails if router.rbac.create=true but serviceAccountName not set\n339: - [ ] imagePullSecrets only rendered when values are provided\n340: - [ ] Helm lint passes with 0 errors\n341: - [ ] Rendered YAML validates with kubectl dry-run\n342: \n343: ---\n344: \n345: ## File Changes Summary\n346: \n347: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n348: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n349: | `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` | Create | ~20 | Chart metadata (name, version, appVersion) |\n350: | `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | Create | ~80 | Default configuration values |\n351: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` | Create | ~50 | Named template helpers |\n352: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | Create | ~100 | WorkloadManager Deployment + Service |\n353: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | Create | ~100 | Router Deployment + Service |\n354: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | Create | ~80 | WorkloadManager RBAC (SA, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) |\n355: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Create | ~50 | Router RBAC (conditional) |\n356: | `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Create | ~60 | Volcano scheduler (conditional) |\n357: | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | Create | ~150 | AgentRuntime CRD |\n358: | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | Create | ~150 | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n359: \n360: ---\n361: \n362: ## Implementation Notes\n363: \n364: ### Chart.yaml Structure\n365: \n366: ```yaml\n367: apiVersion: v1\n368: name: agentcube\n369: description: A Helm chart for AgentCube\n370: type: application\n371: version: 0.1.0\n372: appVersion: 1.0.0\n373: keywords:\n374:   - agentcube\n375:   - kubernetes\n376:   - sandbox\n377:   - ai-agents\n378: maintainers:\n379:   - name: volcano-sh\n380:     email: volcano-sh@example.com\n381: sources:\n382:   - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n383: ```\n384: \n385: ### _helpers.tpl Named Templates\n386: \n387: ```yaml\n388: {{- define \"agentcube.name\" -}}\n389: {{- default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n390: {{- end -}}\n391: \n392: {{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n393: {{- if .Values.fullnameOverride -}}\n394: {{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n395: {{- else -}}\n396: {{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride -}}\n397: {{- if contains $name .Release.Name -}}\n398: {{- .Release.Name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n399: {{- else -}}\n400: {{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n401: {{- end -}}\n402: {{- end -}}\n403: {{- end -}}\n404: \n405: {{- define \"agentcube.labels\" -}}\n406: app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n407: app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n408: app.kubernetes.io/version: {{ .Chart.AppVersion }}\n409: app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Release.Service }}\n410: {{- end -}}\n411: \n412: {{- define \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" -}}\n413: app: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n414: {{- end -}}\n415: ```\n416: \n417: ### Required Value Validation Pattern\n418: \n419: ```yaml\n420: {{- if not .Values.redis.addr }}\n421: {{- fail \"redis.addr must be provided\" }}\n422: {{- end }}\n423: ```\n424: \n425: ### Conditional RBAC Rendering Pattern\n426: \n427: ```yaml\n428: {{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\n429: {{- if not .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n430: {{- fail \"router.serviceAccountName must be set when router.rbac.create is true\" }}\n431: {{- end }}\n432: # RBAC resources...\n433: {{- end }}\n434: ```\n435: \n436: ---\n437: \n438: ## Implementation Timeline\n439: \n440: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n441: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n442: | Phase 1: Foundation | T1.1-T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n443: | Phase 2: WorkloadManager | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n444: | Phase 3: Router | T3.1-T3.9 | Pending | 0% |\n445: | Phase 4: RBAC | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n446: | Phase 5: Volcano Scheduler | T5.1-T5.3 | Pending | 0% |\n447: | Phase 6: CRDs | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n448: | Phase 7: Validation | T7.1-T7.3 | Pending | 0% |\n449: | Phase 8: Tests | T8.1-T8.8 | Pending | 0% |\n450: \n451: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/47 tasks)**\n452: \n453: ---\n454: \n455: ## References\n456: \n457: - Design: `changes/AR-030/design.md`\n458: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\n459: - Proposal: `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`\n460: - deployment/design.md — Reference implementation details\n461: - ci-cd/design.md — E2E Helm usage patterns\n462: - Helm 3 Documentation — Chart structure, templates, values best practices\n463: - Kubernetes API Reference — Deployment, Service, RBAC schemas\n\n(End of file - total 463 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-030 — H